  "remarks": "QDe.153. Money exchange business in Albu Kamal (Al-Bukamal), Syrian Arab Republic, facilitating the movement of funds on behalf of Islamic State in Iraq and the Levant (ISIL), listed as Al-Qaida in Iraq (QDe.115). Used exclusively for ISIL-related transactions. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 8 November 2022.; Listing: Listed by the 1267 Committee on 20 Jul. 2017 ( amended on 8 Nov. 2022 )",
